{"id":292542,"url":"http://bgm.tv/subject/292542","type":2,"name":"天晴爛漫！","name_cn":"天晴烂漫！","summary":"19世纪宣告结束，20世纪拉开帷幕的时代……\r\n虽是天才但社交性为0的技师空乃天晴，与虽然实力高超但却胆小的武士一色小雨，由于遭遇事故而从日本漂流到了美国。\r\n为了回到日本，身无分文的两人选择的方法是参加“美国大陆横断赛车”。\r\n起点是西海岸洛杉矶，终点是纽约。\r\n他们开着自己造的蒸汽汽车，与疯狂的对手互相竞争，从不法之徒和大自然手中保护自己……\r\n究竟两人能否在残酷的比赛中得到优胜，夺得赏金回到故乡呢！？","air_date":"2020-04-10","air_weekday":5,"rating":{"total":175,"count":{"1":0,"2":1,"3":0,"4":4,"5":13,"6":42,"7":76,"8":35,"9":1,"10":3},"score":6.8},"rank":2677,"images":{"large":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/9a/8f/292542_egJkJ.jpg","common":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/9a/8f/292542_egJkJ.jpg","medium":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/9a/8f/292542_egJkJ.jpg","small":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/s/9a/8f/292542_egJkJ.jpg","grid":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/g/9a/8f/292542_egJkJ.jpg"},"collection":{"wish":278,"collect":18,"doing":711,"on_hold":70,"dropped":73},"crt":[{"id":72511,"url":"http://bgm.tv/character/72511","name":"空乃天晴","name_cn":"空乃天晴","role_name":"主角","images":{"large":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/bd/5c/72511_crt_v3u3M.jpg?r=1578280949","medium":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/m/bd/5c/72511_crt_v3u3M.jpg?r=1578280949","small":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/s/bd/5c/72511_crt_v3u3M.jpg?r=1578280949","grid":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/bd/5c/72511_crt_v3u3M.jpg?r=1578280949"},"comment":15,"collects":3,"info":{"name_cn":"空乃天晴","alias":{"kana":"そらの あっぱれ","romaji":"Sorano Appare"},"gender":"男"},"actors":[{"id":7772,"url":"http://bgm.tv/person/7772","name":"花江夏樹","images":{"large":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/6e/6f/7772_prsn_X9rqz.jpg?r=1538803084","medium":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/m/6e/6f/7772_prsn_X9rqz.jpg?r=1538803084","small":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/s/6e/6f/7772_prsn_X9rqz.jpg?r=1538803084","grid":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/6e/6f/7772_prsn_X9rqz.jpg?r=1538803084"}}]},{"id":72512,"url":"http://bgm.tv/character/72512","name":"一色小雨","name_cn":"一色小雨","role_name":"主角","images":{"large":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/9e/ec/72512_crt_7PmO7.